description:
The Bivreost Gold Card will be a great addition to the opportunities that open up in our extension! The complete collection includes 300 branded cards. Here are some benefits for our holders.

— Exclusive design.
— System avatar for web extension.
— 50% chance to get access to the token pre-sale on the Bivreost launchpad.
— Binding and synchronization with Telegram contacts.

The user can hold multiple Bivreost gold cards.
